metadata.description: Sentinels are a community of security experts & hackers who showcased their expertise by uncovering bugs In SocketDL. As a testament to their security prowess, they will be honoured with ranks - Sentry, Defender, and Paladin! They will be integral in shaping SocketDL with a security-first perspective and bring a community centric approch to interop security!
metadata.name: SocketSentinels Wave-1
